%h4 Welcome to Savonia Kassi!
.welcome_text
  %p
    This is Savonia's own Kassi community, where students and staff members can recycle their unnecessary items by selling, lending, renting or giving away. You can also ask and offer small favors, organize ridesharing or rent a student flat.

  %p
    You can help to make Kassi a better service by sharing your thoughts and suggestions with the 
    = link_to("feedback", "#", :id => "give_feedback_link")
    button.